Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:01.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ We
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:03.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Are the Crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:04.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Gems
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.86,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ We'll always save the day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:09.86,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,Steven: ♪ And if you think we can't, we'll ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:12.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Always find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ That's why the people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Of this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:18.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Garnet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:19.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,Amethyst: ♪ Amethyst
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.37,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl: ♪ And Pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:27.91,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,And Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:30.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,棒!\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,停车技术不错,狮子!\NGreat job parking,Lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘛,有点歪就是了\NEh.It's a little crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当我没说,挺不错的!\NNever mind.It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:43.09,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,把狮子停在这里真的好吗?\NIs Lion gonna be okay parked out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:45.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,当然 我把他锁上就好了\NOh, yeah. Uh, I just gotta lock him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:50.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,别担心,他不会到处跑的\NDon't worry. He's not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.97,0:00:54.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我还是不敢相信\NI still can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:56.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这是你第一次进来图书馆\Nthis'll be your first time inside of a library.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.21,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,怎么讲?\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:01.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,因为图书馆里都是你最喜欢的东西\NBecause libraries are full of your favorite thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:09.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,都是书啊!\NBooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘘!\NShh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:14.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}都是书啊!\NBooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.29,0:01:17.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好吧,是时候干掉这些书了\NAll right. Time to beat these books.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:20.10,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啊 你跟它们有什么仇?\NAh. What'd they do to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:22.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我是想提前准备下七年级的课程\NI'm mainly trying to get a head-start on seventh grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:26.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们会学很多新课程,所以\NWe'll be covering a lot of new stuff, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我想提前做好准备\NI just want to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:30.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你用手机查资料不就好了吗?\NCan't you just use your phone to look stuff up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:33.24,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,上一次我用互联网查资料后\NLast time I relied on the Internet for info,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:36.08,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我写出了一篇漏洞百出的,额...\NI ended up writing a very, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:39.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,关于浣熊有热视线能力的文章\Nerroneous paper about raccoons having heat-vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:41.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,浣熊有热视线?!\NRaccoons have heat vision?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘘!\NShh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:44.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我学习的时候你到处看看吧\NYou should take a look around while I get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:47.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这里有一堆你肯定会喜欢的东西\NThere's tons of stuff here I'm sure you'll love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好滴,一会儿见\NOkie. B-R-B.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,纪实类?野\NNonfiction? Wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:57.87,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇哦\NWow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:59.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,就连最下层的架子上也有很酷的书!\NThere's even cool books on the bottom shelves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:02.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哈?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:04.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛呢,小家伙?\NWhat are you doing down here, little buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.78,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,没有书名!\NIt's blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:10.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇!\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:15.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,康妮!\NConnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:17.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看!\NLook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:19.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,没有书名啊\NIt's blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:21.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这是大副巴蒂巴德威克的笔记!\NIt's the journal of first mate Buddy Buddwick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-你是说,这是真货?-当然!\N-Like, the real thing? -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:26.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,杰米表演过关于巴蒂的话剧\NJamie did a play about how Buddy helped
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:28.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他帮助第一任市长发现了海滩市!\N the first Mayor Dewey discover Beach City!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:30.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这里甚至有关于宝石建筑的画!\NThere's even drawings of gem locations in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.93,0:02:32.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,我的天!\NOh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.30,0:02:34.10,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,别管作业了\NForget homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:35.74,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们从头开始看吧!\NLet's take it from the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:36.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,棒!\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,在万幸躲过了死亡的命运后\NAfter narrowly escaping certain doom,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:45.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,威廉杜威船长和我,大副巴蒂\NCaptain William Dewey and I, his first mate Buddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:48.08,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,找到了海滩市这片陆地\Nfounded the land of Beach City.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:52.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,杜威船长刻下了功勋--好吧,是铸造的--\NWith Captain Dewey's legacy cemented -- well, bronzed --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:55.09,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我在想我的功绩会是什么\NI wondered what my legacy would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:58.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,会有后人记住我的名字吗?\NWould anyone remember my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:03:03.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还是会被时间的海浪冲刷的无影无踪呢?\NOr will it be washed away by the ocean of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:05.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我把巴蒂想象成是杰米愁容满面的样子\NI'm picturing buddy as Jamie being all sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.37,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,不错,他入戏的样子\NOh, yeah. Drama zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不!吾辈不能就这么消失!\NNo! I shall not disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:14.21,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,吾辈不会以大副的身份逝去!\NI shan't die a lowly first mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:17.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,吾辈会用一生达成伟业!\NI schwill do something great with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:20.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我将探索全球以求名留青史!\NI'll comb the world in search of greatness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,从此开启了我人生的新篇章--\NAnd so began a new chapter of my life --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,即探索先前未探索之事物\Nto explore the previously unexplored
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.86,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,在世界上留下吾之印记!\Nand to make my mark on the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,旅途持续了若干个日夜\NI traveled for many days and nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:36.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,直到,最终,我到达了某种田地\Nuntil, finally, I found myself in a field of sorts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:39.87,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,倒不如说,是某种战地\Nor, should I say, a field of swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这里散布着巨大的,香甜的草莓\Nintermingled with giant, sweet-smelling strawberries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,和人脑袋一样大\Nas big as one's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:47.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,“谁能握持如此巨大的武器呢?”我细细思考\N"Who could have wielded such a weapon?" I pondered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.01,0:03:51.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,“又有什么样的战争用到了这样的武器呢?”\N"What sort of battle could this have been used for?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.38,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我绞尽脑汁\NI contemplated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:57.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我不停地速写,沉浸在深思当中\NI continued to sketch, sinking into deep concentration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:00.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,突然我感到一只熟悉的手的触摸\Nwhen I suddenly felt the touch of a familiar hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,侬好\NAhoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,向您请安\NSalutations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,原来是两只水晶战士\NIt was two of the Crystal Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,宝石们以前应该穿着不一样吧\NWould the Gems have looked different back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:10.17,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对,肯定的\NYes. Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,原来是两只宝石战士\NIt was two of the Crystal Gems
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她们曾经从海怪那救下了船长\Nthat had saved my captain from a sea beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们现在是来救你的\NAnd now we're here to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是我没有陷入危险啊\NBut I'm not in peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:21.74,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我只是个卑微的旅者,只求名字能\NI'm just a humble traveler who wants my name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,被后世的所有人所记住\Nto be remembered by everyone for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:28.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这个嘛,不要在此逗留,旅者\NWell, travel not here, traveler,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.25,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,只因此地十分危险\Nas this place is very dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.32,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好吧,我去别的地方\NVery well. I'll go elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.35,0:04:33.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等等!\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,地球上还有很多地方\NThere are many places on this Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,像你这样的人类不应该造访\Nthat a human like you should avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:39.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我给你标记了这些地方以便查找\NHere's a convenient marking of all the places
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:43.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这些地方你绝对,任何情况下,都不能去\Nwhere you should absolutely, under no circumstances, visit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不然你短暂的生命会更短暂\Nif you'd like to keep your short life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:48.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,只有最勇敢,最无畏,\NOnly the bravest, most courageous,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:51.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,最值得铭记的探险家才敢\Nmost memorable explorers would dare
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,到这些美妙的地方探索\Nto visit these fascinating places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:57.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对,我刚刚才说过\NYes, that's essentially what I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.85,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不管怎样,还好我给你点明了\NAnyway, glad we cleared that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.08,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,再了个见! \NFare thee well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:05.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对啊,如果我探索了这些地方\NSurely,if I do explore these places,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我将会以勇敢和无畏被人铭记!\NI'll be remembered as brave and courageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.91,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他还画了通讯中心\NHe drew the communication hub.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,闪闪鼻涕虫?\NSparkling slugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他怎么想到这些名字的?\NWhere'd he get these names from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦!这个名字他猜对了! \NOoh!He got this one right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,感觉好像又去了一遍这些地方\NI feel like I'm back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方?\NWhat's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:42.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这个我也不知道\NI don't know this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:46.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦!看起来他还去了宝宝基地!\NOoh! It looks like he went to the kindergarten!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我发现自己身处一个最令人惊讶的地方\NI found myself at the most amazing locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:53.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯,很尖\NHmm.Very pointy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:56.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是我还是隐约有种感觉\NThough I could not shake the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:06:00.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,感觉这次旅行有什么...不对劲\Nthat something about this journey felt a bit...off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我很好奇为什么这些小洞会在这儿\NI wonder why all these tiny caves are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-嘿,伙计!\N-Hey, Buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.35,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对-对就是我\NTh-This is Buddy speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,从我的洞里出来\NGet out of my hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:15.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗟乎,原来是第三只水晶战士\NLo, it was the third Crystal Gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.53,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你是,呃,住在这里?\NDo you, uh, live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,以前是!\NUsed to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:21.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,现在我就是不时回来\NNowadays, I just come back every so often
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:23.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看看家人怎么样了\Nto see how the fam's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.37,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,家人? \NThe fam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿,最近怎样啊?\NHey, how you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.54,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗷!你是不是长高了?\NAw!You getting taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.14,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃,等我一下,有个客人来了\NUh, give me a sec --I have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.14,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你来这儿干啥?!\NWhy are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:37.21,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,我的错 来,我给你看看\NOh. My apologies. Here, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.58,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我现在是作为探险家在进行环球探险\NI've been traveling the globe as an adventurer and explorer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.02,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,赞!\NNeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.38,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我一直在旅途中\NI've been on a journey to discover
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:45.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,探索无人曾到达的地方\Nplaces no one has ever been before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.32,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是看这个地方的样子\NBut by the looks of this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,很多人已经来过这里了\Nmany people have been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:52.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等下,这张地图是你自己做的?\NHold on. Did you make this map?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是你的同僚帮我标记的\NIt was drawn up for me by your compatriots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.13,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,就是说,噗\NSo, pbht!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你又独立发现了什么呢?\NWhat have you discovered on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这个嘛,我...发现了...\NWell, I uh..That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:03.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,呃 哦 天啊\NOh. Uh...Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:07.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这张图上没有一处是我自己发现的!\NI haven't discovered a single thing on this map!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:08.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,就是说啊,哥们\NYeah, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:11.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你只是在跟着别人的足迹旅行罢了\NYou're just following someone else's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.01,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,原来这就是我\NAnd here I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,自诩为伟大的冒险家和探索者\Nclaiming to be a great explorer and adventurer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:18.02,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但自己其实只是...\Nwhen all I really am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.05,0:07:19.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,只是个游客!\Nis a tourist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇 别当着我面儿伤心啊\NWhoa.Don't get all sad on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:29.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,怪不得我感觉有什么不对劲!\NThis is why my journey hasn't felt right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.60,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,额\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.60,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃,哦,对了!\NUh, oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.47,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你为什么不去试试找沙城堡呢?\NWhy don't you try and find the sand castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃,啥? \NUh, wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.54,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,一边去,我给你指下\NOut of the way. I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:45.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,它就在这片全都是沙的地方\NIt's right around here in this sandy area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.61,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-真的?-当然!\N-Really? -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,人说它永远不会停在一个地方\NThey say it's never in the same place twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,它总是在沙漠各地不断重建\NIt's always rebuilding itself all over the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,听起来是个再合适不过的探险了!\NThat sounds like the perfect adventure for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我还将会是第一个看到它的人!\NAnd I'll be the first one to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呵 好吧\NHeh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:01.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的帮助 再见!\NThank you for your help. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,欢迎随时回来!\NCome back anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.53,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但也别太频繁!\NBut not too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:13.04,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我已经在这片沙漠中漫步了10天了\NI've been wandering this desert for 10 days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:16.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我想我该脱下探险家之大衣\NI suppose I could take off my explorer's coat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好歹能凉快一会\Nfor a bit of relief,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:20.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是如果我不穿大衣的话,人们看到我就会想\Nbut if I wasn't wearing this, people would see me and think,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:24.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,"哦,就是个普通人到处走而已\N"Oh, just some man wandering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:25.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,一点都不重要\NNot important at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:29.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,可不是嘛,他连神秘的沙城堡都找不到!"\NWhy, he can't even find the elusive sand castle!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:32.09,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,“哈哈哈”他们会这么笑\N"Ha, ha, ha" they'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:35.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,“真是个傻瓜”他们会这么说\N“What a fool," they'd continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃\NUgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:40.47,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这就是了---这就是我冒险旅途的尽头\NThis is it, then -- the end of my adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:44.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我跟着一张地图来到了我的终结之地\NI've just followed a map to my own end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:48.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这就是我逝去前所能看到的最后一幕--\NAnd this will be the last thing I ever see as I expire --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:52.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,一个天使和她的--一、二、三--\Nan angel and her -- one, two, three --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好几只狮子,来取走我的灵魂\Nseveral lions, here for my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这就完结了吗?\NIs this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我猜是的\NI guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.49,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦等下,后面还有一堆呢!\NOh, wait. There's a bunch more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我慢慢恢复了意识\NAs I slowly regained consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:06.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我看到了一个高大的人影\NI became aware of a large figure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.53,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是个巨大的女人\Nin the shape of a giant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她卷曲的秀发\NThe ringlets of her hair
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:13.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,铺满了她的肩和背\Nspilled over her shoulders and back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:15.70,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,就像一丛玫瑰\Nlike a swath of roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.04,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,妈妈!\NMom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:19.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿 你还好吗?\NHey. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:22.61,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我意识到自己被包围在她的...\NI realized I was surrounded by her pack of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,七只狮子?\NSeven lions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,求求你--别吃我!\NPlease -- don't eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:29.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,别担心 我们没有恶意\NOh, don't worry. We mean no harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:31.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那就好\NThat's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃\NUgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:35.49,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们人类为什么要来这种地方?\NWhat brings a human out to a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:38.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我以前是船上的大副,但是我们已经找到了陆地\NI was a first mate on a ship, but we found land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,然后我意识到自己并不想呆在那片陆地\NAnd then I realized I didn't want to stay in that land,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所以我就去找其他陆地\Nso I went to find more land.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,然后有人说不要去找那片陆地\NBut then I was told not to find that land
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.37,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,因为太危险了\Nbecause it was really dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.34,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是我想证明自己所以...\NBut I wanted to prove myself and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.61,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这样,我把全部都写在这儿了\NLook. I wrote it all down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:52.71,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,为什么我要费劲去找沙城堡\NWhy am I looking for the sand castle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:55.34,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,它甚至可能根本就不存在!\Nthat probably doesn't even exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-沙城堡?-对啊\N-A sand castle? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.68,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我已经在沙漠中搜寻了数周\NI've combed these deserts for weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,根本连影子都没看到\Nand there's been no sign of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那个不就是吗?\NWould that be a sign of one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:07.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那就是了!我一定要记录下来!That's it! I've gotta record this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我一定要--等下\NI've got to -- Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:13.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你先看见的 所以根本就不算数!\NYou saw it first. This doesn't count at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:15.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我真是个糟糕的探索者\NI'm a terrible explorer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.60,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,吃了我吧 我就这点用处了\NEat me. It's all I'm good for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:21.54,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等等,等等,你说的不对\NNow, now, that's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:25.17,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当然,这些地方确实有前人探索过\NSure, all these places have been explored before,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:27.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但是从未有人以如此亲切的语言记载过\Nbut they haven't been recorded so intimately
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:30.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,像这笔记里那样\Nas they have been in this journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:33.35,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你的记载使得这些地方又变得新鲜和特殊\NIt makes them new and special all over again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:36.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所有读者都会有同感\Nfor any reader to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你有没有想过当个作家?\NHave you ever considered becoming an author?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:42.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这样我就成为了一名作家\NAnd become an author I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我指如疾风,写出了一本又一本书\NI wrote up a storm, making book after book,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:49.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我意识到如此多的书,可以填满一座图书馆!\Nso many until I realized I could fill a library with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.37,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我知道了!\NI get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,就是巴蒂巴德威克图书馆!\NThe Buddy Buddwick Library!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘘!\NShh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:58.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他确实在这镇上留下了印记\NHe really did leave a mark on this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.54,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇 等一下\NWhoa. Hold the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.21,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他就长那个样子吗?\NIs that what he looked like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:05.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们的想象错到家了\NWe imagined him way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我还是喜欢我们的版本\NI kind of liked our version better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:10.72,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我也是\NMe, too.
